textAfterTable: 7 Songs Customer Reviews it was okaaayyy :/           by i<3tft well im a pretty big fan of there for tomorrow and i have all of their albums but this ep was a little hard to swallow. the first song, small world is AMAZING!!! i really loved it. that one and the soul full solace interlude are my favorites, but the others took a little more time to get used to. at first i thought 'how can they ruin themselves like this???' but now i see that these are pretty good remixes and that not a lot of bands can pull it off, and now i finally have realized what a good job there for tomorrow has done :) so in the end if you like dub-step and there for tomorrow, you should get it. well at least small world or soul full solace XP Props           by Kemalo95 There For Tomorrow should stick to their style of music
